The '''British International School of Zagreb''' ('''BISZ''') is a British [[international school]] in [[Zagreb]], [[Croatia]].<ref>"[http://www.britishschool.hr/eng/contacts/ Contact]." British International School of Zagreb. Retrieved on April 30, 2015. "Address: Dedići 102 Zagreb, Croatia 10000"</ref> It is a sister institution of the ''Kreativan razvoj'' Primary School. First opening on September 2, 2013,<ref>"[http://www.britishschool.hr/eng/about/who-we-are/54/ WHO WE ARE]." British International School of Zagreb. Retrieved on April 30, 2015.</ref> the school is scheduled to include years 1-13.<ref>"[http://www.britishschool.hr/eng/programmes/ PROGRAMMES]." British International School of Zagreb. Retrieved on April 30, 2015.</ref>

